---
const components = [
  {
    title: 'Streaming price feeds',
    description:
      'Request a dataline to stream real time price updates. Fast local queries with pre-aggregated bars - from 5 seconds to yearly intervals. Extended hours and pre-market included.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Direct broker access',
    description:
      'Bring your own broker. Your cash and assets stay in your name, at your broker — not held by a intermediary platform that could freeze withdrawals or collapse overnight. Direct connection gives you full real time control over execution and positions.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Signal engine',
    description:
      'Technical indicators, financial metrics and market signals collected for your universe of instruments. Vectorised computation, instant access. Need a custom indicator? Add it to the computation pipeline.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Risk engine',
    description:
      'Kill switches and position controls activate when conditions are met - drawdown limits, volatility thresholds or earnings proximity without P&L buffer. Parameterise your rules once and let the system hold the line',
  },
  {
    title: 'Deploy trading agents',
    description:
      'Run a trading desk of autonomous agents. Code their workflow natively in Python: when to scan, when to enter, how to size, when to exit. Register each agent on the platform with its own capital allocation and risk rules. Monitor and intervene at any point: pause, stop, or kill and flatten all positions.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Smart triggers',
    description:
      'Directly plan a trade using conditional triggers. Chain them across entry, add, reduce, and exit to orchestrate the full lifecycle. Glasshouse watches the conditions and submits orders only when they are met — keeping your levels hidden from the book until execution.',
  },
];
---

<section id="architecture" class="px-6 py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-text-primary sm:text-4xl">
      What's behind the glass
    </h2>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-center text-text-secondary">
        End-to-end orchestration, from signal to close. Scan technical and fundamental signals, analyse price action, size positions, manage risk, execute orders, monitor exposure — and scale out when conditions change.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      {components.map((component) => (
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-accent/10 bg-bg-elevated p-8 transition-colors hover:border-accent/30">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-accent">{component.title}</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-text-secondary">{component.description}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
